    "body": "@davidkna thank you!\nI have an additional question. How does one get the $status and $CMD_DURATION values of the command just executed and use them in the transient prompt? As far as I can tell, status gets set again between the command ran and when it gets to `starship_transient_prompt_func` so it would not reflect the right status, and cmd_duration is shown on the next transient prompt, after the current prompt/transient prompt. I'm not sure why this is the case, and I would like the status and command duration of the command ran to be shown on the transient pompt of that command.",
